            %p
              %strong Video blender
              is developed to offer the most effective advertising of your product in the internet. Using
              %strong 99% automatic process
              we offer advertising services on different nternet platforms and search engines. The main particularities are:
            %p
              %strong - Geo-targeting (local orienting)
            %p
              %strong - Dealer Tagging

            %p Try interactive demo-version of our production. Choose some settings for Video blender such as: projects to use, youtube channel settings, youtube video settings. See estimated results; how videos will look like using settings choosed by you.
            .btn_middle_block
              = link_to sandbox_client_path(client_uuid), target: "blank", class: "try-btn" do
                TRY BLENDER VIDEO
      .col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-3

  %section.section_2#blender_images
    .container-fluid
      .row
        .top-row= image_tag "/assets/sandbox/home_page/Line_1.png", class: "img-responsive line1"
      .row
        .col-lg-5.col-md-6.col-sm-12#blender-img-pn1
          .ff-container.ff-responsive
            %canvas.ff-canvas.ff-canvas-active{width: "1000", height: "562"}
            %img.my_class_3.freezeframe-responsive.ff-setup.ff-image.ff-image-ready{src: "/assets/sandbox/home_page/image-blending.gif", data: {play: "pause"}}
            .ff-overlay
        .col-lg-7.col-md-6.col-sm-12#blender-img-pn2
          .row
            .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-middle
              %h1.text-center.blender-img BLENDER IMAGES
              %p.text-right Image Blender is developed for advertising your product on social networks using professional advertising images. Whole the process is automatic, offering a fast speed of image production and distribution. By pressing the button "Try Image Blender" you will be able to test our image production. Choose liked design projects, images, icons and market messages to use and after that see the estimated result (blended image) of our production.
              .btn_middle_block
                = link_to 'javascript://', class: "try-btn coming_soon_popover", id: "try-blender-images", type: "button", value: "pause" do
                  = "TRY BLENDER IMAGES"
            .col-md-6.col-sm-6= image_tag "/assets/sandbox/home_page/Image_2.png", class: "img-responsive sp-image2"

